  "comment": "Showtec Performer Cyc Q6: The Showtec Performer Cyc Q6 is a silent 180 W RGBALC Cyclorama Wash with high CRI, suitable for theaters and film/photo studios. It is often used to create the illusion of air, open space or great distance in the back of the stage. By using a single row of these advanced background washers you can create powerful and homogeneous lighting for a height of up to 6 meters.\n\nThe Performer Cyc Q6 is suitable for temporary outdoor use and can be controlled manually as well as via DMX. Of course, it is also equipped with simple controls and built-in programs that ensure a good workflow.",
